      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Kelly Tolhurst was appointed  Parliamentary Under Secretary of State at the Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy on 19 July 2018.</p>
</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_4928">
            <h1 id="parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-small-business-consumers-and-corporate-responsibility">Parliamentary Under Secretary of State, Minister for Small Business, Consumers and Corporate Responsibility</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>Responsibilities include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Industrial Strategy</li>
  <li>small business and enterprise (including access to finance)</li>
  <li>consumer and competition (including competition law)</li>
  <li>labour markets</li>
  <li>postal affairs (including Royal Mail)</li>
  <li>corporate governance</li>
  <li>insolvency</li>
  <li>retail sector</li>
  <li>cross-government work on loneliness</li>
</ul>

<p>The minister also has temporary responsibility for the following areas:</p>

<ul>
  <li>professional services</li>
</ul>

</div>
            <div class="read-more">
                <a href="/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state--61">More about this role</a>
                <p class="js-hide-other-departments organisations-name-list">
  <a class="organisation-link" href="/government/organisations/department-for-business-energy-and-industrial-strategy">Department for Business, Energy & Industrial Strategy</a>
</p>

            </div>
</section>      </div>

